    "title": "読書少女と賢者の催し物",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日、図書室に本を返しに来たところ――",
            "enText": "One day, I came to the library \nto return a book.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "pathId": 7257069515895761493,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "――それで、あの……\r\n今年の『読書推進週間』で\n図書委員が行う催し物なんですが……。",
            "enText": "—so, you know… is what the library committee \nwill be doing this year for \"Reading \nPromotion Week\"…",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 142,
                    "pathId": -4563019952498225838
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 143,
                    "pathId": 7195876818662384723
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -966301966299361171,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "図書委員のウマ娘A",
            "enName": "Librarian Horsegirl A",
            "jpText": "うーん。例年通り、\r\n図書新聞増刊号の展示だけでいいんじゃない？",
            "enText": "Hmmm. Why don't we just display the extra \nissues of the library newspaper as usual?",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -62760055798224136
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -7796358281284893471
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8379282048329950374,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "図書委員のウマ娘B",
            "enName": "Librarian Horsegirl B",
            "jpText": "気持ちはわかるけど、\r\n興味がない子がほとんどだしなぁ……。",
            "enText": "I know how you feel, but most of \nthe kids aren't interested…",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 3916647614347963915
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 6549794143519024466
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 7143639259247050507
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4314535240009975302,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "で、でも、本に触れてもらえる\r\nいい機会だと思うんですが……。",
            "enText": "And yet, I think it's a great opportunity \nfor people to be exposed to books…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8160060622368255744
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": 2194795721415429346
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 1948568214212520536
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2643459139947075235,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "……はぁ。\r\n結局、決まらなかったなぁ。",
            "enText": "… Huh. In the end, I couldn't decide.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "『読書推進週間』の準備、大変そうだな",
                    "enText": "Preparing for \"Reading Promotion Week\" \nsounds like a lot of work.",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "『読書推進週間』の準備、大変そうだね",
                    "enText": "Preparing for \"Reading Promotion Week\" \nsounds like a lot of work.",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 2858331771407180576
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": -6694093345350013296
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -377130603007163751,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "え？\r\nあ、えっと――",
            "enText": "What? Uh, well…",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 59,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -2880496868263089365
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": 8806634781304634257
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1908598601203027579,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ゼンノロブロイに事情を聞いたところ、\r\n『読書推進週間』の催し物に対し、\n図書委員たちはあまりやる気がないらしい。",
            "enText": "I asked Zenno Rob Roy about the situation, \nand she said that the library committee \nmembers were not very enthusiastic about the \n\"Reading Promotion Week\" event.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 157,
                    "pathId": 1068672502546238494
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 167,
                    "pathId": 3333587229522829265
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5512347056517258219,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "『読書は難しそう』と催し物に興味を持つ子\r\n自体が少なくて……図書委員としても\n力を入れる意味はないという意見が多く――",
            "enText": "There were many comments that \"reading seems \ndifficult\" and that there was no point in \nthe book committee making an effort because \nthere were few children who were interested \nin the event.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 123,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": 6312467604961054300
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 134,
                    "pathId": -4793585125004662485
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8299731307916431975,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "でも……難しそうで終わってしまうのは、\r\nもったいないし……とても寂しいです。",
            "enText": "But it would be a shame and… very sad if it \nended up being too… difficult.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 85,
                    "pathId": 703397139956998182
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -3448967191697645554
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3591867748382299563,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "童話、ロマンス、英雄譚――本を読めば、\r\nどんな世界にだって飛んでいける……。",
            "enText": "Fairy tales, romance, heroic tales - read a \nbook, and you can fly to any world…",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": -8413270128171732779
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": 6608063691809511329
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 155,
                    "pathId": -2714740077068657083
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 139,
                    "pathId": -2742389103795878517
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8904640486108733338,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "可愛らしいお姫様や勇敢な英雄にもなれる。\r\n夢の世界への入り口なのに……！",
            "enText": "You can be a pretty princess or a brave \nhero. You're a gateway to a dream world…!",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -5353494263646836744
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -8635316661688788526
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5194226252722930551,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "たしかに、難しい本もありますけど……\r\n素敵で楽しいものもたくさんあるってことが\nわかれば、きっと――",
            "enText": "Yes, some books are difficult to read, \nbut if you know that there are many \nwonderful and fun books on… you will \nbe able to find them.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "催し物でそれを伝えればいいんじゃないか？",
                    "enText": "Why don't we just tell them \nthat at the event?",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "催し物でそれを伝えればいいんじゃない？",
                    "enText": "Why don't we just tell them \nthat at the event?",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 156,
                    "pathId": -5474078949526109029
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 153,
                    "pathId": -4819019095609285459
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": 4757807595174907977
