            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スイープトウショウ",
            "enName": "Sweep Tosho",
            "jpText": "魔法の物語も一緒に紹介すれば、\r\nみんな魔法の素晴らしさに気づくはずだもの！",
            "enText": "If you introduce the story of \nmagic together, people will realize \nhow wonderful it is!",
            "nextBlock": 19,
