        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "はい……っ！\r\n本の魅力を伝えるためなら、\nどんな練習でもお付き合いします……！",
            "enText": "Yes…! I'm willing to go along with any \nexercise to make the book more appealing…!",
