        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "それに……日頃、図書室で助けて\r\nいただいているお礼もしたかったですし。",
            "enText": "In addition, I wanted to thank you \nfor your help at the… library.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
